# runs/

This directory contains benchmark run artifacts — `run.json`, per-candidate outputs, traces, and scores.

Run artifacts are generated by the GoblinBench Runner CLI and are gitignored by default.

Directory structure:
```
runs/<run-id>/
  run.json                    — Overall run result
  candidates/
    <candidate-id>/
      output.json             — Raw candidate output
      trace.jsonl             — Execution trace
      scores.json             — Scorer results
      artifacts/              — Candidate-produced files
```
